OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FGuernsey's education department will
OL,8,Fprovide staff to Sark School as more
OL,9,Fdetails emerge over the sudden
OL,10,Fdeparture of its former headteacher.
OL,12,FMichelle Brady was sacked earlier this
OL,13,Fyear for failing to disclose her son's
OL,14,Fconviction for child sex offences -
OL,15,Falthough there is no suggestion that
OL,16,Fany Sark children were affected by
OL,17,FJacob Brady's crimes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
