CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FITV Channel understands that six other
OL,8,Fmembers of the school's staff are
OL,9,Fleaving this summer, putting the
OL,10,Feducation of its students at risk.
OL,12,FIt has prompted the island's
OL,13,Fgovernment, the Chief Pleas, to
OL,14,Fformally request support from the
OL,15,FGuernsey Education Office.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Office has
OL,18,Fconfirmed that it will supply two new
OL,19,Fteachers, including an Executive Head
OL,20,FTeacher for the equivalent of one day
OL,21,Fa week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FThey also clarified that Sark will
OL,8,Fcover staffing costs.
OL,10,FThe latest staff departures were
OL,11,Frevealed at a recent meeting of Chief
OL,12,FPleas. ITV News understands that there
OL,13,Fwere also new details surrounding Mrs
OL,14,FBrady's removal as headteacher.
OL,16,FIn February, Michelle Brady's son was
OL,17,Fconvicted of sexual offences against
OL,18,Fchildren and jailed for four years and
OL,19,Ffour months.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FWhile Mrs Brady was not under any
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation, she was
OL,9,Fsuspended almost a week following the
OL,10,Fconviction and was later removed from
OL,11,Fher post.
OL,13,FITV News now understands that Mrs
OL,14,FBrady had not disclosed her son's
OL,15,Ftrial or conviction to the Board of
OL,16,FGovernors or Chief Pleas' Education
OL,17,Fdepartment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
