PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FIt is also understood that Jacob Brady
OL,8,Fhad accompanied his mother on several
OL,9,Fschool trips with the children,
OL,10,Fincluding one overnight stay.
OL,12,FIt has previously been confirmed to
OL,13,FITV News that Jacob Brady's offences
OL,14,Fare not related to Sark or Sark School.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
