PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,FA statement from Sophie Roughsedge,
OL,8,FHead of Operations for Education,
OL,9,Freads: "Following discussions this
OL,10,Fpast term, the Guernsey Education
OL,11,FOffice received a formal request from
OL,12,Fthe Government of Sark for support
OL,13,Ffrom the beginning of the new academic
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,F"We have agreed to provide two
OL,17,Fteachers, including a lead teacher, to
OL,18,Fsupport Sark School for the upcoming
OL,19,Facademic year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784909938
OL,3,CIsland school's future at risk as
OL,4,Cstaff leave following headteacher's
OL,5,Csacking
OL,7,F"Although Sark falls outside Guernsey
OL,8,FEducation Office's formal remit, our
OL,9,Fpriority is always to make sure every
OL,10,Flearner across the Bailiwick has
OL,11,Faccess to the best possible education.
OL,13,F"Parents, staff and pupils at Sark
OL,14,FSchool can be reassured that we are
OL,15,Fworking hand-in-hand with Sark's
OL,16,FEducation Committee and Sark School to
OL,17,Fput strong foundations in place now,
OL,18,Fto secure a stable, positive future
OL,19,Ffor the school, and to minimise any
OL,20,Fimpact to its pupils."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
